### Special Events API Tests

@host = http://localhost:8086/api

### Create a new Demande (Teacher ID: 101)
POST {{host}}/demandes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titre": "Conférence sur la Cyber-sécurité",
  "objectif": "Sensibiliser les étudiants aux menaces actuelles",
  "debutEvent": "2026-03-10T09:00:00.000+00:00",
  "finEvent": "2026-03-10T12:00:00.000+00:00",
  "nbreLimitParticipant": 50,
  "enseignantId": 7
}

### Get All Demandes (Admin View)
GET {{host}}/demandes

### Update Status (Admin Validation)
# Note: Replace {id} with the ID from the previous POST response
@demandeId = 2
PATCH {{host}}/demandes/{{demandeId}}/status?status=VALIDE

### Delete Demande
DELETE {{host}}/demandes/{{demandeId}}
